cast.overview: Washed-up MMA fighter Cole Young, unaware of his heritage, and hunted by Emperor Shang Tsung's best warrior, Sub-Zero, seeks out and trains with Earth's greatest champions as he prepares to stand against the enemies of Outworld in a high stakes battle for the universe.
cast.title: Mortal Kombat

also_known_as: シシィ・ストリンガー
details.biography: Sisi Stringer is an actress and assistant director, known for Mortal Kombat (2021), Bloody Hell (2020) and Carnifex.
details.name: Sisi Stringer
details.place_of_birth: Byron Bay, New South Wales, Australia
